metadata.name: Sad boys don't fold
metadata.description:
If I were a painter,  
he would definitely be my muse.  
But amidst the shades  
of black, gray, and blue  
there wouldn't be  
a color dark enough  
to match the sadness  
in his eyes.

- Raven

Still , we don't fold. behind his closed eyes burn a sea of passion , a relentless decision to keep going , for that's all we can do.
